[42.454741, "o", "\r\n"]
[43.04508, "o", "\r\n  Analysis Report\r\n  ==================================================\r\n  Status: analyzed\r\n  Contribution ID: 6616bd76-1101-4a...\r\n  Campaign Match: Yes\r\n  Summary: Your IOCs match 8 indicators seen by other organizations. Associated threat actors: LockBit. Campaigns: lockbit-3.0-healthcare.\r\n  Shared IOCs: 8\r\n  Threat Actors: LockBit\r\n\r\n  Actions (3):\r\n"]
[43.045209, "o", "    [CRITICAL] Block C2 domains/IPs at firewall and DNS\r\n           5 network IOCs match known LockBit infrastructure seen across multiple orgs\r\n    [HIGH] Hunt for related activity in your environment\r\n           Cross-reference the 8 matched IOCs with your SIEM/EDR logs for the last 30 days\r\n    [MEDIUM] Share findings with your sector ISAC\r\n           Campaign correlation suggests coordinated activity — sector-level sharing accelerates collective defense\r\n\r\n"]
[44.077926, "o", "  \r\n"]
[44.889206, "o", "\r\n  >>> Campaign Match: Yes. 8 shared IOCs. LockBit healthcare campaign.\r\n"]
[46.103861, "o", "  3 other hospitals saw the same C2 domain and attacker IP.\r\n"]
[46.915458, "o", "  Ohio learned this in seconds — would take days through an ISAC.\r\n"]
[50.737089, "o", "\r\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\r\n  \"What is our CrowdStrike missing?\"\r\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\r\n"]
[52.752819, "o", "  Ohio mapped the attack to MITRE ATT&CK. CrowdStrike caught T1486\r\n"]
[53.565874, "o", "  (encryption) but what else did it miss? Other hospitals know.\r\n"]
