[58.130585, "o", "\r\n  Analysis Report\r\n  ==================================================\r\n  Status: analyzed\r\n  Contribution ID: 5c612ae2-81e7-40...\r\n  Coverage Score: 46%\r\n  Detection Gaps: 7\r\n    - T1021.001: Remote Desktop Protocol\r\n"]
[58.130673, "o", "    - T1490: Inhibit System Recovery\r\n    - T1070.001: Clear Windows Event Logs\r\n    - T1562.001: Disable or Modify Tools\r\n    - T1003.001: LSASS Memory\r\n\r\n  Actions (5):\r\n    [CRITICAL] Deploy T1021.001 detection\r\n           Add detection rule for Remote Desktop Protocol. No known tool detections — consider custom Sigma rule.\r\n    [HIGH] Deploy T1490 detection\r\n           Add detection rule for Inhibit System Recovery. No known tool detections — consider custom Sigma rule.\r\n    [HIGH] Deploy T1070.001 detection\r\n           Add detection rule for Clear Windows Event Logs. No known tool detections — consider custom Sigma rule.\r\n    [MEDIUM] Deploy T1562.001 detection\r\n           Add detection rule for Disable or Modify Tools. No known tool detections — consider custom Sigma rule.\r\n    [MEDIUM] Deploy T1003.001 detection\r\n           Add detection rule for LSASS Memory. No known tool detections — consider custom Sigma rule.\r\n\r\n"]
[59.161095, "o", "  \r\n"]
[59.974171, "o", "\r\n  >>> 46% coverage. 7 detection gaps found.\r\n"]
[61.185383, "o", "  T1490 (VSS deletion) — CRITICAL. CrowdStrike misses it.\r\n"]
[61.997097, "o", "  T1021 (RDP lateral movement) — missed across all tools.\r\n"]
[62.810723, "o", "  Ohio knows exactly what detection rules to deploy NOW.\r\n"]
