[73.292725, "o", "  Category Avg: 9.0\r\n  Percentile: 50th\r\n\r\n  Actions (2):\r\n    [MEDIUM] Supplement CrowdStrike with additional detection rules\r\n           CrowdStrike has known gaps in: T1041, T1070.001, T1490, T1562.001, T1048. Consider custom Sigma rules or a complementary tool.\r\n    [INFO] CrowdStrike scores at or above average\r\n           Your score (9.2) vs category average (9.2). Address known gaps to maximize value.\r\n\r\n"]
